156
00:08:04,706 --> 00:08:08,912
All you need is your intelligence
and your determination to succeed.

157
00:08:09,112 --> 00:08:12,969
Trying to help the poorest in this
world is a strong motivation.

158
00:08:13,169 --> 00:08:13,907
However,

159
00:08:14,107 --> 00:08:18,200
it is essential to keep our goal
in mind at all times,

160
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:22,289
